{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01SBTUDysa16D7XRaidZjjsx","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the knowledge file against the source file carefully.\n\n**V1: Omission Check**\n\nGoing through the source file section by section:\n\n1. **Overview section**: The source mentions this widget outputs checkboxes for \"処理対象レコード選択用ボタン\" as defined in \"UI標準 UI部品 テーブル\". The knowledge file captures the essence but omits the specific \"UI標準 UI部品 テーブル\" reference. This seems minor but might be acceptable as it's a reference to another document.\n\n2. **コードサンプル**: Both design artifact (local) and implementation artifact (server) code samples are present in the knowledge file. Looks complete.\n   \n3. **仕様**: The spec section covers the checkbox behavior in input screens and the \"●\" mark display in confirmation screens. The attribute table is complete with all properties documented. For the `toggle` attribute, the source specifies that when set to true, \"全選択\" and \"全解除\" links appear in the title area enabling bulk selection operations—this detail appears to be captured in the knowledge file.\n\nHowever, I notice the knowledge file documents the default value as false and mentions the bulk selection/deselection capability when true, but it's missing the constraint note \"(一括選択/解除は不可)\" which clarifies what happens when toggle is false. This constraint information could be important for implementation.\n\n4. **内部構造・改修時の留意点**: The part list is complete. Looking more closely at the toggle attribute definition, I need to verify the exact wording—the source shows toggle with default false and a note about what happens when true, but I want to make sure the full constraint documentation is captured. toggle パラメータの動作を確認している。デフォルト値が false のときは一括選択/解除ができず、true に設定するとタイトル部に「全選択」「全解除」リンクが表示されるということだ。ナレッジファイルはこの挙動を正しく捉えているが、false のときの制限について明示的に記載されていない。\n\nname 属性も確認したが、ソースと一致している。ナレッジファイルの属性